# 🎯 Flexbox CSS Layout Project

This project demonstrates how to build **modern, responsive layouts** using **CSS Flexbox**.  
Flexbox simplifies the process of aligning, distributing, and ordering elements within a container, making it a powerful tool for web developers.

## 📌 Features
- ✅ Fully responsive layout using Flexbox  
- ✅ Easy alignment (horizontal & vertical)  
- ✅ Space distribution without using floats or positioning hacks  
- ✅ Clean and minimal code structure  
- ✅ Beginner-friendly examples  

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **HTML5** – For semantic structure  
- **CSS3 (Flexbox)** – For layout and styling  

## 📂 Project Structure
flexbox-layout/
│── index.html # Main HTML file
│── style.css # Flexbox styling
│── images/ # Project images
│── README.md # Project documentation

